Package ca.uqac.lif.cep.ltl.bitmaps

Implementation of the LTL operators as functions on bitmaps.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BinaryBitmapProcessor
    Abstract processor implementing a binary bitmap connective or operator.
    BitmapAnd
    Bitmap implementation of logical conjunction.
    BitmapF
    Bitmap implementation of the LTL "future" operator.
    BitmapG
    Bitmap implementation of the LTL "globally" operator.
    BitmapImplies
    Bitmap implementation of logical implication.
    BitmapNot
    Bitmap implementation of logical negation.
    BitmapOr
    Bitmap implementation of logical disjunction.
    BitmapU
    Bitmap implementation of the LTL "until" operator.
    BitmapX
    Bitmap implementation of the LTL "next" operator.
    BitmapXor
    Bitmap implementation of logical "exclusive or".
    CollectBitmap
    Collects a stream of Boolean values into a bitmap.
    Main
    A "dummy" main class; it is only there to make the generated JAR runnable from the command line.
    ReleaseBitmap
    Releases the contents of a bitmap into a stream of Boolean values.
    UnaryBitmapProcessor
    Abstract processor implementing a unary bitmap connective or operator.
